RockyBot: News Research Tool with Gemini + Streamlit
RockyBot is a GenAI-powered web app that lets you analyze and query news articles using Google's Gemini API, LangChain, and Streamlit. It supports URL-based document loading, embeddings with FAISS, and smart Q&A retrieval with sources.


Features
Enter up to 3 article URLs
Extracts, splits, and indexes the content
Ask natural language questions about the articles
Uses Gemini (Gemini 1.5 / 2) for contextual answers
Displays source citations

Project Structure
gen_ai_proj/
